title: Ep. 60: Pro Bowl Snubs, MVP Odds, and Playoff Scenarios With Robert Mays and Danny Kelly
description:
The Ringer's Robert Mays and Danny Kelly discuss Pro Bowl roster snubs (6:00), who the real MVP is (18:00), the best-case-scenario playoff matchups (28:00), and the most impactful Christmas Day games (40:00).
